title: Ibby's Falafel
typeOfFood: Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small eatery, mostly take-out. Offers various vegetarian and vegan items. Veg sandwich, lemony tart & crunchy pita fatoush salad, veggie combo platter, stuffed grape leaves, Turkish coffee, desserts baked on site. Opens daily 10-12am.
